{"tid":43614,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"毒男網戀被騙近27萬　看新聞才知中招！！！","createTime":"2016-12-17T15:30:15.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T08:03:09.000Z","uid":34714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9e2ea34fe110f144d1c12e2ba3fe59cb39fc0fe0","tid":43614,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:30:15.000Z","msg":"據悉，被騙的24歲男事主，無業，早前透過手機交友程式「lihkg」，認識一名聲稱外貌可愛甜美少女，兩人其後發展成「網上情侶」。女方曾要求男事主送贈多隻羊仔，男事主花費約1.7萬元購買相關物品後郵寄到外國地址。其後女方以不同借口向事主索取羊仔，男事主先後5次按指示，將價值合共約25萬元羊仔郵寄至5個外國地址。<br />\n<br />\n男事主於上月開始與女方失去聯絡，當時仍未為意遇上騙徒，直至昨晚看到有關網上情緣騙案的新聞報道，始思疑受騙，今日凌晨約1時到九龍城警署報案。"},{"pid":"0237b9a352d95a108f32063d269171655abe089f","tid":43614,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:31:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b7318d32b529729d53b4439c2374e8bf559b95","tid":43614,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:36:53.000Z","msg":"羊b <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd582eff14a3c63eed7d25ac451ca6efe3e85c5","tid":43614,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:39:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cac5177d37292b37d1cb6a99fc4daa0c1a9ec99","tid":43614,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T15:40:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>羊b <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2b0fff7e63dc735fb6cd7091574976a320a4b1","tid":43614,"uid":22820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT